<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Quiz dos Pequenos Exploradores</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Baloo+2:wght@700;800&family=Fredoka:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/btn-voltar.css">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: 'Fredoka', 'Baloo 2', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #3bb273 0%, #00CFFF 100%);
      background-attachment: fixed;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }
    .bg-figma {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100vw;
      height: 100vh;
      z-index: 0;
      background: url('/img/tcc.img/tela inicio.png') center center/cover no-repeat;
      opacity: 0.18;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity 0.4s;
    }
    .pagina-central {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 4.5em auto 0 auto;
      padding: 2.5em 2em 2.5em 2em;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.93);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 32px 0 rgba(60, 180, 115, 0.10), 0 1.5px 8px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.7s;
    }
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .quiz-titulo {
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'Baloo 2', 'Fredoka', Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.2em;
      color: #00CFFF;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 1.2em;
      margin-top: 0.5em;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    .quiz-desc {
      font-size: 1.18em;
      color: #3bb273;
      font-family: 'Fredoka', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 1.5em;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .quiz-lista {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 2em;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 2em;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .quiz-card {
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #fffbe7 60%, #FFD600 100%);
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
      padding: 1.5em 1.2em 1.5em 1.2em;
      min-width: 220px;
      max-width: 300px;
      width: 100%;
      transition: box-shadow 0.18s, transform 0.18s;
      border: 1.5px solid #FFD600;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.7s;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .quiz-card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px 0 rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.13), 0 2px 8px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      transform: scale(1.04);
    }
    .quiz-card h2 {
      color: #00CFFF;
      font-size: 1.25em;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 0.5em;
      font-family: 'Baloo 2', Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .quiz-card p {
      color: #3bb273;
      font-size: 1em;
      margin-bottom: 1em;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .btn-destaque {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FFD600 0%, #3bb273 100%);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      font-weight: 700;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 0.7em 1.7em;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      transition: background 0.18s, transform 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s;
      margin-top: 0.5em;
      outline: none;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      appearance: button;
      font-family: 'Baloo 2', 'Fredoka', Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .btn-destaque:after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0; top: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 #FFD600;
      transition: box-shadow 0.18s;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .btn-destaque:focus {
      outline: 2px solid #FFD600;
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }
    .btn-destaque:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3bb273 0%, #FFD600 100%);
      transform: scale(1.07);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px 0 rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.18), 0 2px 8px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.13);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .btn-destaque:active {
      filter: brightness(0.97);
      transform: scale(0.98);
    }
    .quiz-card a.btn-destaque {
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: none;
      background: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .quiz-card .btn-destaque {
      margin-top: 1em;
    }
    /* Remove underline and link style from anchor */
    .quiz-card a.btn-destaque, .quiz-card a.btn-destaque:visited {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: none;
      background: none;
    }
    /* Make anchor look like button */
    .quiz-card a.btn-destaque > span {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FFD600 0%, #3bb273 100%);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      font-weight: 700;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 0.7em 1.7em;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      transition: background 0.18s, transform 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s;
      outline: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      font-family: 'Baloo 2', 'Fredoka', Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .quiz-card a.btn-destaque:hover > span {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3bb273 0%, #FFD600 100%);
      transform: scale(1.07);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px 0 rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.18), 0 2px 8px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.13);
    }
    .quiz-card a.btn-destaque:active > span {
      filter: brightness(0.97);
      transform: scale(0.98);
    }
    .quiz-aviso {
      color: #FFD600;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 1.5em;
      margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .pagina-central {
        max-width: 98vw;
        padding: 1.2em 0.2em 2em 0.2em;
      }
      .quiz-lista {
        gap: 1em;
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .pagina-central {
        margin: 1.2em auto 0 auto;
        padding: 0.7em 0.1em 1.2em 0.1em;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }
      .quiz-titulo {
        font-size: 1.25em;
      }
      .quiz-card {
        min-width: 90vw;
        max-width: 98vw;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bg-figma"></div>
  <button class="btn-voltar" onclick="window.history.back()" aria-label="Voltar" style="z-index: 11000; position: fixed; top: 0.5em; right: 0.5em; left: auto;">
    <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
      <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="22" fill="#00CFFF"/>
      <polygon points="30,14 18,24 30,34" fill="#0077B6"/>
      <ellipse cx="38" cy="38" rx="2.5" ry="1.5" fill="#B2F7EF"/>
    </svg>
  </button>
  <div style="height: 32px;"></div>
  <main class="pagina-central">
    <h1 class="quiz-titulo">🌳 Quiz dos Pequenos Exploradores 🌎</h1>
    <p class="quiz-desc">Teste seus conhecimentos sobre natureza, meio ambiente, biomas e animais! Ganhe moedinhas e prêmios a cada acerto! 🪙🏆</p>
    <div class="quiz-lista">
      <div class="quiz-card">
        <h2>Quiz: Animais do Brasil 🦜</h2>
        <p>Descubra curiosidades sobre a fauna brasileira!</p>
        <a href="/quiz/animais" class="btn-destaque"><span>Jogar</span></a>
      </div>
      <div class="quiz-card">
        <h2>Quiz: Biomas do Mundo 🌍</h2>
        <p>Teste seus conhecimentos sobre florestas, desertos, oceanos e mais!</p>
        <a href="/quiz/biomas" class="btn-destaque"><span>Jogar</span></a>
      </div>
      <div class="quiz-card">
        <h2>Quiz: Meio Ambiente ♻️</h2>
        <p>Aprenda sobre reciclagem, preservação e sustentabilidade!</p>
        <a href="/quiz/meioambiente" class="btn-destaque"><span>Jogar</span></a>
      </div>
      <div class="quiz-card">
        <h2>Quiz: Curiosidades da Natureza 🌱</h2>
        <p>Responda perguntas divertidas sobre plantas, clima e ecossistemas!</p>
        <a href="/quiz/natureza" class="btn-destaque"><span>Jogar</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="quiz-aviso">Mais quizes em breve! Continue explorando e aprendendo! 🚀</div>
  </main>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
